\newlabel{fig:in_transform}{{3}{8}{The Intersecting-to-Nonintersecting (I-N) transformation. A configuration $C$ capable of satisfying both Job 1 and Job 2 is duplicated into job-specific replicas $v_{C,1}$ and $v_{C,2}$ in strictly disjoint clusters, connected by a zero-cost edge}{figure.caption.3}{}}
