\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces The theoretical restricted reverse construction. By generating disjoint dummy tools for specific configurations, the SSP transition metric $b - |C_u \cap C_v|$ can be engineered to match integer GTSP edge weights. This construction requires exponential time to encode a full graph.}}{10}{figure.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:dummy_tools}{{4}{10}{The theoretical restricted reverse construction. By generating disjoint dummy tools for specific configurations, the SSP transition metric $b - |C_u \cap C_v|$ can be engineered to match integer GTSP edge weights. This construction requires exponential time to encode a full graph}{figure.caption.4}{}}
